==English==
===Verb===
'''appearing'''
# Present participle of ''to [[appear]]''.
#To become visible.
#:The ghost had a way of '''appearing''' and then disappearing before you could be sure what you had seen.''
#[[seeming|Seeming]], not actual.
#:''The water, though '''appearing''' to be deep, was really only inches in depth.''
#Formally present
#:''The famous rock star will be '''appearing''' at the club for only one show.''